    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You are going to absolutely love this ride! It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
