    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system overhauled with upgraded seals and hub bolts. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting a climate-controlled life.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
