      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom-fresh condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and displays a level of care seldom seen on the secondary market. The exterior paint retains its original deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The factory-correct alloy wheels are pristine, without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and transparent service history performed exclusively by certified specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is an investment-grade example for a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
