      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior, mirroring its original showroom state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning driver a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in truly superlative condition.",
