    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and looks even more stunning in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43800.0,
