    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, maintained to an exacting mechanical standard. The S54B32 power plant delivers linear torque through its individual throttle bodies, with the variable VANOS system operating within factory tolerances. This example features a reinforced rear subframe carrier and documented rod bearing replacement, addressing critical chassis and internal longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, coupled with a factory M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and original dampers. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the exterior retains its factory-correct paint depth and high-gloss finish. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
